Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來是桓尾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 10分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10分 嘛 還算穩妥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這班等級很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生後第一次交到了女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其名為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人太怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 無可奈何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女朋友的名字叫卜部美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2話 謎之羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新開的咖啡店 聽說凍糕挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋了啊 上野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那裏的肉和女孩的胸部一樣柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 上野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 我說如果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果交到女朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你交到女朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我說如果 只是假設而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 戀人一般最初會做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初？ 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽手之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手 手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 可以牽你的手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有牽手的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用那麼果斷地拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然開始交往一個月左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是像戀人一般的進展完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 要說唯一一樣像戀人的行為的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天在回家路上分別時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會稍微舔些卜部的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼椿 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還沒牽過手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有這個日課 卜部不會缺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初之前 要做啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 最初之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽手之前做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你交到女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交到女朋友了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽手之前 先搭話 打聽下興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再聊聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 興趣之類的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 聊聊卜部的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是運動啊 樂器演奏啊 畫畫之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好張開拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自椿的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著做了椿花的剪畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是啥 為什麼能做到這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥內褲上別著剪刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你問為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明就只有這點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我覺得在男人面前 若無其事地露出內褲不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿的話 被看到了我也無所謂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內褲？剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣就算交流了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 弄完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 內褲上別著剪刀是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 內褲？ 剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天想你做麵包…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫到這裏可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的是白色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜 卜部？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常刺激的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初之前再之前要做啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 那個最初之前再之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒啦 在牽手和交流更前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在糾結這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對交到女朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對交不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是啥 是啥是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然是…打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開頭是最重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊拉 日安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}天氣不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招呼不是跟誰都會打的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙絕對沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 第一次見面的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的情況是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫椿明 有什麼不明白都可以問我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那是我們獨特的招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內褲上別著剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖 要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在這裏分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我在平時那橋上等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 沒做平常的日課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是因為我拒絕了糖而生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說忘記了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張開嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 忘掉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 甜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 別擅自抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 雖然突然抱過去是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用發動內褲剪刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是卜部的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣才能做些更像戀人間做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-PART
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久之前你拜託我的電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 完全忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz12.792\pos(620,405)}ScieNce Boy aNd Magic GirL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這可能用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行 這行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 好好說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想過要不要和你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為其他事情順便先看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我那張電影票也給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你好好說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這個 這周週日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不嫌棄的話我想和你一起去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 這週日我有預定 去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是卜部的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得我們開始交往到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件像戀人之間會做的事情都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 明明我們之間有著羈絆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羈絆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水就是我和椿的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 站起來 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就給你證明這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要稍稍繞下路 能和我走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 擅自進去沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 能坐在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 我想要你和我約定一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你在我說能睜開眼之前一直把眼睛閉著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛？ 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須這樣 肯答應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你把眼睛閉起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 把嘴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要把帶著我的口水的手指放進椿的嘴裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的口水很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔了卜部的口水之後心臟的跳動突然變得很劇烈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 心臟跳得很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不由地很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體非常地熱對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼卜部會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  感覺臉上濕濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為椿流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼椿的身體會出現這種變化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 椿剛才舔的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我心跳很厲害的時候的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳很厲害的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔了我心跳很厲害的時候的口水之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼椿也會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 椿是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水是我們之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天做了稍有點特別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借此簡單明瞭地來證明了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 可以把眼睛睜開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 心臟還跳得很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也擔心椿會打破約定 把眼睛睜開
